---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Meridian AI Search - Answer-Market Operating Briefs"
  description="Answer-market operating briefs and AI search monitoring for B2B companies whose buyers ask AI before they talk to sales."
>
  <style>
    .ai-page {
      --ink: #e6edf3;
      --muted: #8b949e;
      --line: #30363d;
      --panel: rgba(21, 25, 34, 0.86);
      --panel-strong: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.92);
      --green: #8be9a8;
      --blue: #8fd3ff;
      --purple: #d7b7ff;
      --orange: #ffbe89;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #080d13 0%, #0d1117 44%, #080d13 100%);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
    }

    .ai-wrap {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .ai-hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
      display: grid;
      align-items: end;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(8, 13, 19, 0.98) 0%, rgba(8, 13, 19, 0.86) 48%, rgba(8, 13, 19, 0.24) 100%),
        url('/images/ai-search-hero.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .ai-hero-inner {
      padding: 120px 0 72px;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .ai-kicker,
    .ai-label {
      color: var(--green);
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .ai-hero h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      max-width: 11.5ch;
      font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.8rem);
      line-height: 0.92;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .ai-hero p {
      margin-top: 24px;
      max-width: 680px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .ai-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .ai-primary,
    .ai-secondary,
    .ai-plan button {
      min-height: 46px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .ai-primary,
    .ai-plan button {
      background: var(--green);
      color: #081019;
      border: 0;
    }

    .ai-primary:hover,
    .ai-plan button:hover {
      background: #b6f4c8;
    }

    .ai-secondary {
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1px solid rgba(143, 211, 255, 0.42);
      background: rgba(8, 16, 25, 0.66);
    }

    .ai-band {
      padding: 64px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .ai-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .ai-panel,
    .ai-plan,
    .ai-proof {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035), rgba(255,255,255,0.012));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .ai-panel h3,
    .ai-plan h3,
    .ai-proof h2,
    .ai-system h2,
    .ai-sample h2 {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .ai-panel p,
    .ai-plan p,
    .ai-proof p,
    .ai-system p,
    .ai-sample p,
    .ai-plan li {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .ai-proof {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .ai-proof h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .ai-system h2,
    .ai-sample h2 {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .ai-math {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .ai-metric {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 18px;
      background: rgba(8, 13, 19, 0.48);
    }

    .ai-metric strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .ai-metric span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .ai-plans {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .ai-plan {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    .ai-plan.featured {
      border-color: rgba(139, 233, 168, 0.8);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(139, 233, 168, 0.25), 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    }

    .ai-plan .price {
      margin: 16px 0 4px;
      font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .ai-plan .price small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .ai-plan ul {
      margin: 18px 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      flex: 1;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .ai-plan li::before {
      content: "•";
      color: var(--green);
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }

    .ai-plan input {
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: rgba(8, 13, 19, 0.78);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .ai-plan input::placeholder {
      color: #6e7681;
    }

    .checkout-error {
      display: none;
      color: #ff9a9a;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .checkout-error.visible {
      display: block;
    }

    .ai-system,
    .ai-sample {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .ai-list {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .ai-list li {
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(48, 54, 61, 0.72);
      padding-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .ai-sample pre {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      color: var(--blue);
      background: rgba(8, 13, 19, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 22px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    .ai-small {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .ai-grid,
      .ai-plans,
      .ai-math {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .ai-proof,
      .ai-system,
      .ai-sample {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .ai-hero {
        min-height: auto;
        background-position: 62% center;
      }

      .ai-hero-inner {
        padding: 104px 0 54px;
      }

      .ai-hero h1 {
        max-width: 8.5ch;
        font-size: clamp(2.55rem, 10.4vw, 3.15rem);
      }

      .ai-hero p,
      .ai-actions {
        max-width: 320px;
      }

      .ai-actions {
        width: min(320px, calc(100vw - 72px));
      }

      .ai-actions {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .ai-actions a {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .ai-grid,
      .ai-plans,
      .ai-math {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="ai-page">
    <section class="ai-hero">
      <div class="ai-wrap">
        <div class="ai-hero-inner">
          <div class="ai-kicker">Meridian AI Search</div>
          <h1>Own the answers before buyers reach your site.</h1>
          <p>
            Meridian turns buyer questions into answer-market operating briefs: which prompts matter, who AI systems name, what sources shape the answer, and which asset to publish next.
          </p>
          <div class="ai-actions">
            <a class="ai-primary" href="#plans">Start with a diagnostic</a>
            <a class="ai-secondary" href="#system">See the system</a>
            <a class="ai-secondary" href="#sample">See the brief</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="system" class="ai-band">
      <div class="ai-wrap">
        <div class="ai-label">product thesis</div>
        <div class="ai-grid">
          <div class="ai-panel">
            <h3>Not cheap SEO software</h3>
            <p>AI answers now shape vendor shortlists before the visitor reaches your site. This is executive-grade answer intelligence for teams where one deal is worth thousands.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-panel">
            <h3>Productized by default</h3>
            <p>Every customer runs through the same prompt map, competitor table, source-gap analysis, and action queue. You get a sellable brief instead of open-ended consulting.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-panel">
            <h3>Built to compound</h3>
            <p>Prompt sets, source patterns, content fixes, and category benchmarks compound across categories. The signal gets better as the system sees more answer surfaces.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ai-band">
      <div class="ai-wrap">
        <div class="ai-proof">
          <h2>The expensive question is not "what is our rank?"</h2>
          <div>
            <p>
              The expensive question is: when a buyer asks ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, or Google AI which vendors to compare, do they see you, your competitors, or a source that frames the category without you?
            </p>
            <p>
              Meridian packages that answer into a recurring brief: prompt coverage, source influence, competitor pressure, and a prioritized asset queue. No dashboard ceremony. No monthly slide theater.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="plans" class="ai-band">
      <div class="ai-wrap">
        <div class="ai-label">plans</div>
        <div class="ai-plans">
          <form class="ai-plan checkout-card" data-plan="diagnostic">
            <h3>Diagnostic</h3>
            <p>Paid entry point for teams that want a useful answer-market brief before recurring spend.</p>
            <div class="price">$750 <small>one-time</small></div>
            <ul>
              <li>10 buyer questions</li>
              <li>3 competitors</li>
              <li>Source-gap diagnosis</li>
              <li>30-day asset queue</li>
            </ul>
            <input name="name" required placeholder="Name" />
            <input name="email" required type="email" placeholder="Work email" />
            <input name="website" required type="url" placeholder="https://company.com" />
            <button type="submit">Start diagnostic</button>
            <p class="checkout-error"></p>
          </form>

          <form class="ai-plan checkout-card featured" data-plan="monitor">
            <h3>Monitor</h3>
            <p>Self-serve recurring monitoring for teams that want the brief refreshed as the answer surface moves.</p>
            <div class="price">$500 <small>/mo</small></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Weekly AI answer checks</li>
              <li>Prompt and competitor drift</li>
              <li>Source-gap watchlist</li>
              <li>Monthly asset queue</li>
            </ul>
            <input name="name" required placeholder="Name" />
            <input name="email" required type="email" placeholder="Work email" />
            <input name="website" required type="url" placeholder="https://company.com" />
            <button type="submit">Start monitor</button>
            <p class="checkout-error"></p>
          </form>

          <form class="ai-plan checkout-card" data-plan="operator">
            <h3>Operator</h3>
            <p>Productized execution guidance without open-ended consulting.</p>
            <div class="price">$1,000 <small>/mo</small></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Deeper prompt library</li>
              <li>Content and schema briefs</li>
              <li>Implementation-ready fixes</li>
              <li>Priority report turnaround</li>
            </ul>
            <input name="name" required placeholder="Name" />
            <input name="email" required type="email" placeholder="Work email" />
            <input name="website" required type="url" placeholder="https://company.com" />
            <button type="submit">Start operator</button>
            <p class="checkout-error"></p>
          </form>

          <form class="ai-plan checkout-card" data-plan="partner">
            <h3>Partner</h3>
            <p>Premium tier for when direct operator work is worth the constraint.</p>
            <div class="price">$2,500 <small>/mo</small></div>
            <ul>
              <li>Everything in Operator</li>
              <li>Monthly strategy review</li>
              <li>Implementation prioritization</li>
              <li>Limited availability</li>
            </ul>
            <input name="name" required placeholder="Name" />
            <input name="email" required type="email" placeholder="Work email" />
            <input name="website" required type="url" placeholder="https://company.com" />
            <button type="submit">Apply for partner</button>
            <p class="checkout-error"></p>
          </form>
        </div>
        <p class="ai-small">Checkout is live through Stripe. The first brief is generated after onboarding; recurring plans keep the brief fresh as sources and competitors move.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ai-band">
      <div class="ai-wrap ai-system">
        <div>
          <div class="ai-label">operating system</div>
          <h2>What happens after checkout.</h2>
          <p>
            The product starts with your domain, category, competitors, and buyer questions. Meridian turns that into a repeatable evidence run and a prioritized asset queue.
          </p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ai-list">
          <li>Customer submits domain, category, competitors, and buyer questions on the onboarding page.</li>
          <li>Meridian runs the category through the same answer-market pipeline each cycle.</li>
          <li>The output is a compact operating brief: prompts, competitors, sources, gaps, and fixes.</li>
          <li>Only Partner customers get direct operator involvement; everyone else improves the product data set.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="sample" class="ai-band">
      <div class="ai-wrap ai-sample">
        <div>
          <div class="ai-label">sample output</div>
          <h2>A compact operating brief, not another dashboard to babysit.</h2>
          <p>
            Each run is built around buyer questions, answer mentions, source gaps, competitive pressure, and the assets most likely to change what AI systems say next.
          </p>
        </div>
        <pre>QUESTION
Which AI governance platforms should a financial services team compare?

ANSWER SURFACE
You: omitted
Competitor A: recommended
Competitor B: cited by third-party guide

SOURCE GAP
Your integration page is strong, but AI systems cite neutral comparison pages and implementation checklists first.

NEXT FIX
Publish a comparison page with schema, add implementation-risk language, and earn two neutral category references.</pre>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.checkout-card').forEach((form) => {
      form.addEventListener('submit', async (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();
        const el = event.currentTarget;
        const error = el.querySelector('.checkout-error');
        const button = el.querySelector('button');
        const data = new FormData(el);
        error.classList.remove('visible');
        button.disabled = true;
        button.textContent = 'Opening checkout...';

        try {
          const resp = await fetch('/api/create-checkout', {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
            body: JSON.stringify({
              plan: el.dataset.plan,
              name: data.get('name'),
              email: data.get('email'),
              website: data.get('website'),
              source: 'ai-search',
            }),
          });
          const json = await resp.json();
          if (!json.url) throw new Error(json.error || 'Checkout failed');
          window.location.href = json.url;
        } catch (_) {
          error.textContent = 'Checkout could not start. Email jeremy@bymeridian.com and I will fix it.';
          error.classList.add('visible');
          button.disabled = false;
          button.textContent = 'Try again';
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
